# AI Use Statement

We used ChatGPT as an assistance tool during this project.

ChatGPT was used for:

* understanding some implementation details,
* getting coding and debugging support,
* organizing the Role C planning approach,
* improving code readability,
* preparing concise documentation.

All code was reviewed, executed, and tested locally by the team. The final implementation, experiments, and reported results were produced in our local repository environment.

ChatGPT suggestions were not used directly without checking. We tested the outputs, fixed errors, and kept only the parts that worked correctly for the project.
